commitResults.messageTitle: - Added skeletal greeting with robot name, prompt and exit greeting.
- Added ASCII art for robot name - Added and personalised robot prompt statements - Added functionality of echoing user input - Added exit program when given command 'bye'
- Added comments for code - Added 'list' command for listing all previous user inputs - Removed echoing of user input

- Added Task class for encapsulation and object representation of tasks in the task list - Added extra commands for marking and unmarking tasks in the task list - Updated displaying of task information to include marked/unmarked condition
